per shareholder to send those statements=C2=A0<em>by email</em>? Weird tech=
nology they=E2=80=99ve got going there.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0=
;">Anyway one problem with the recent boom in retail trading is that compan=
ies are sending more of those 25-cent emails. In part because there are mor=
e retail investors, but also because it=E2=80=99s easier for them to buy mo=
re stocks. With commission-free trading and fractional shares, you can buy =
0.5 shares of 100 stocks almost as easily as you can buy 100 shares of one =
